    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "=General= Västra Syninge, along with Jägarhyddan and Norrtjära, is the most developed bouldering area in Roslagen. =Directions= Västra Syninge is located 9 km east of Rimbo, take road 77 towards Finsta (bus 625 from Danderyds sjukhus to Finsta station), then turn left towards Södertjära, travel just over 1 km to the sign for V Syninge on the right. Drive 100 m and park in the clearing on the left. The blocs are lined up down towards the field; Stenkyrkan is visible directly from the road, Hasselblocket is 30 m beyond that and Häggsten a further 200 m on. A path runs through the forest to the left of the field. =Sectors=",
